{
  "_provenance": "schema-derived from exit_triggers DDL (migrations/005_exit_triggers.sql) + AC-V3.1 thresholds. Timestamps are fixed-wall-clock values chosen to test window boundary semantics. Trigger reasons are named constants matching alpha_bot_execution.py triggered_reason strings. No producer-computed floats.",
